caption:
Our factory will be taking a well-deserved break for the Christmas holidays! ✨ 

As a result, all orders placed from December 17th onwards will have a production time of 8 weeks instead of the usual 5 weeks. 

We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause, but even our hardworking factory needs some rest to come back stronger and ready to deliver amazing pieces in the new year. 

Thank you for your understanding and support! ❤️‍🔥
